
	graphDraw

	- graph drawing for undirected graphs

		uses an implementation of the Force-directed Placement algorithm
		as described in Graph Drawing by Force-directed Placement
		http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.13.8444&rep=rep1&type=pdf


	requirements:
	
		- python 2.7
		- PyGame (http://www.pygame.org/hifi.html)


	usage:

		after imported, call the draw(vertex_list, edge_list)

		the vertex_list is a list with instances of the Vertex class
		(as defined in graphDraw.graph)
		
		the edge_list is a list with instances of the Edge class
		(as defined in graphDraw.graph)



